{"tid":1828774,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【100毛】「案件無可疑？」– 柳記職員：阿雲海, 你相信個囚犯是可以「好堅定地」自殺啦！","createTime":"2020-01-18T06:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T14:20:04.000Z","uid":167548,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fbedcb347d5e7ed13401947c5c87c840d4c77b40","tid":1828774,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:49:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100most/videos/174041533807581/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100most%2Fvideos%2F174041533807581%2F&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=cb9dd2d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100most/videos/174041533807581/</a><br />\n<ins><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">案件一、巴藉囚犯因犯連環鳳姐姦殺案入獄</ins></span><br />\n疑點：入獄後仍有姦殺案<br />\n柳記職員：阿雲海, 你相信個囚犯是可以<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">「好堅定地」</span></strong>自殺啦！<br />\n<ins><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">案件二、台灣女子被兩位疑犯謀殺</ins></span><br />\n疑點：大量懷疑假證據<br />\n魔警重案組：拉左一個(被屈)就Close File, 但是有一個潛逃理鳩佢. 查所有想查呢單案o既人<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">案件三、徐步高</span></ins><br />\n雲海：笑鳩你班網民風向180度轉變。<br />\n<br />\n成立香港國際法庭(HongKong Tribunal), 架空現存司法機構是未來要任。<br />\n三權就是合作。馬道立就是法官貴族之惡首。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><ins>一七七六年七月四日，大陸會議<br />\n美利堅十三個聯合邦一致通過的宣言</ins></div><br />\n他拒絕批准建立司法權力的法律，藉以阻撓司法公正。<br />\n&quot;He has obstructed the Administration of Justice by refusing his Assent to Laws for establishing Judiciary Powers.<br />\n<br />\n他控制了法官的任期、薪金數額和支付，從而讓法官完全從屬於他個人的意志。<br />\n &quot;He has made Judges dependent on his Will alone for the tenure of their offices, and the amount and payment of their salaries."},{"pid":"bf427138d60aec441ec6365270dbf6e81d9ad90f","tid":1828774,"uid":167548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:50:40.000Z","msg":"大法官好自為之<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4U8Eng.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4U8Eng.jpg&h=9912fcbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb53939bf75cec1c6b2dd4c5d1096221817e3cd2","tid":1828774,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf427138d60aec441ec6365270dbf6e81d9ad90f","tid":1828774,"uid":167548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:50:40.000Z","msg":"大法官好自為之<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4U8Eng.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4U8Eng.jpg&h=9912fcbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:51:19.000Z","msg":"裁判官葉啟亮 將登上The Magnitsky Act<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1827986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1827986</a>"},{"pid":"ee23a072c65d6fab3ae42df3a020077011304387","tid":1828774,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:52:26.000Z","msg":"真心睇下段片, 講緊香港人被馴化, 再配合華人o既崇拜威權！"},{"pid":"de6d3fd1324e696ed95c09b231d3d4bdf9fbb505","tid":1828774,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:53:28.000Z","msg":"幫我推一下, 得唔得？講緊冰封三尺, 非一日之寒！"},{"pid":"b847718d1bd745c21058ca703630337bd313cf63","tid":1828774,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:58:26.000Z","msg":"雲海<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d531904ef43ae48b49c2a0ab78b1f585f35f220f","tid":1828774,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ef30c7f0487b9b615b1803c6d79744d74efa55","tid":1828774,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:04:58.000Z","msg":"人呢？"},{"pid":"da3910d07be2d58352eb